1.title: Episode #4.1
1.plot: In the world of diesel vehicles, Heavy D, Diesel Dave and their crew at DieselSellerz builds the biggest, baddest trucks around. They work hard - and play harder in the process!

2.title: School is in Session
2.plot: A new client asks for the biggest build yet- a monster school bus capable of driving over sand and water. Redbeard discovers the Mello Yello racecar from Days of Thunder and the perfect buyer for it.

3.title: 2 Wheel Drive
3.plot: No one has more fun or builds bigger, badder trucks than the crew at DieselSellerz. Their mega builds and awesome truck giveaways are the stuff of diesel legend.

4.title: Yo Soy Diesel
4.plot: No one has more fun or builds bigger, badder trucks than the crew at DieselSellerz. Their mega builds and awesome truck giveaways are the stuff of diesel legend.

5.title: Diesel Defender
5.plot: Major league pitcher Jacob deGrom asks them to revamp his OBS Ford, and the diesel guys convert a rare British Land Rover Defender from right hand drive to left hand drive for a client.

6.title: De-Ice Ice Baby
6.plot: The guys convert a rare Land Rover Defender from right hand drive to left. Plus, Heavy D tries to get money for the shop by parting out a military plane de-icer.

7.title: Yes Way, Jose
7.plot: The crew overhaul a truck for a local dad whose F350 broke down. And, they assemble the shop's first-ever diesel motorcycle, with a Magneto!

8.title: Tuff Truck Takedown
8.plot: In the world of diesel vehicles, Heavy D, Diesel Dave and their crew at DieselSellerz builds the biggest, baddest trucks around. They work hard - and play harder in the process!

75.title: Fly Like an Eagle
75.plot: Heavy D and Diesel Dave source an old 1984 AMC Eagle that Heavy D plans to convert to diesel for a future project. They also reminisce on their favorite builds.

1.title: Free Willy's
1.plot: In the diesel world, no one has more fun or builds bigger, badder trucks than Dieselsellerz. They turn a rusty 1948 Willy's Jeep into a diesel-drinking monster for a new client & find the next giveaway truck at a gas station: a pristine LBZ Duramax.

2.title: Tows Before Bros...
2.plot: Heavy D, Diesel Dave and the Dieselsellerz crew scramble to salvage their Duramax giveaway after it goes up in flames. Heavy D ignores Redbeard's strict budget restrictions to turn their company tow truck into a tricked out, lifted monster.

3.title: Hell Camino
3.plot: When The Muscle buys a battered El Camino to fix and flip, it might be too big a job for even the Dieselsellerz team to transform it. Heavy D and Diesel Dave find their next giveaway truck- a Ford F650 that's a perfect platform for pure power.

4.title: Truck Vs. Train
4.plot: Heavy D comes up with a plan to rid the world of minivans by making and selling a mini version of Dieselsellerz' legendary MegaRam. The F650 giveaway reveal will stretch the power of diesel to the limit when the F650 tries to pull an entire train.

5.title: The Hole-y Grail
5.plot: A client asks Heavy D & his crew to turn his beat-up work truck into an off-road mobile service station. Heavy D searches for the next giveaway truck, & Diesel Dave finds the Holy Grail: a 2nd generation, quad cab Dodge with a 12-valve diesel engine.

6.title: From Sweden with Love
6.plot: The Dieselsellerz are cranking out their next giveaway: a quad cab Dodge with a 12-valve. When Black Rhino tools asks the guys for a show-stopping build for a trade show, they pull out all the stops- including importing a surprise from Sweden.

7.title: Abominable SnowRam
7.plot: The Dieselsellerz are pulling out all the stops to build a cool hybrid for their good friend and stunt driver Tanner Godfrey. Meanwhile, time is running out for Heavy D to find a show stopping build for the upcoming SEMA trade show in Vegas.

8.title: Busting at the SEMA
8.plot: Last year the Dieselsellerz put their insane builds on the map when they debuted their legendary MegaRam at the SEMA trade show in Vegas. With less than two weeks to go, it's all hands on deck to finish a 6-wheel drive F550 in time for the big show.

1.title: Callout Fallout
1.plot: When the frame on Heavy D's quick flip unsalvagable, he decides to turn into the ultimate mud truck; Chavis gets more than he bargained for after being invited to bring his custom race truck to the Call Out Challenge truck competition.

2.title: There Will Be Mud
2.plot: Heavy D, Diesel Dave and the Dieselsellerz crew work on finish their epic monster mud truck for the giveaway; The Muscle scrambles to find a buyer for the flashy Denali he bought with Heavy D's permission.

3.title: Feed the Beast-Mode
3.plot: Sick of the ridicule on social media, Heavy D decides to finally finish the "Fail of the Year" UTV. And the gridiron comes to the garage when NFL legend Marshawn Lynch asks the guys to build him a Beastmode UTV.

4.title: Hummer Time
4.plot: When Redbeard challenges Heavy D to repurpose some old inventory, Heavy decides to marry a stretched 6 door F650 with a camper to create the ultimate expedition vehicle. And the guys buy a Hummer H1 from a mysterious mountain man.

5.title: Motors and Rotors
5.plot: Heavy D, and Diesel Dave and the Dieselsellerz crew scramble to finish a six-door stretched F650 Expedition Camper for a big client; Heavy D shocks the team with his latest flip: a diesel-powered experimental helicopter.

6.title: Truck Norris
6.plot: The Diesel Sellerz pick up a vintage fire truck to transform into a tow truck that can carry everyone in the shop; Chuck Norris stops by, seeking a truck for his latest project.

7.title: Epic Fail of the Year
7.plot: The Dieselsellerz pick up a vintage fire truck to transform into a tow truck that can carry everyone in the shop. And Heavy D is determined to finish the endless Fail of the Year UTV build.

8.title: Somersault
8.plot: Heavy D decides to test the physics abilities of the shop and build a somersaulting truck to use for viral videos. And The Muscle takes over a flip from Heavy D and turns a Dodge Ram into a badass modern pop-up camper.

9.title: Flippin' Diesel
9.plot: The Diesel Brothers are up against the clock for their SEMA build- a replica Ford Bronco made from an F350 and an Excursion. Heavy D brings in physics help to make his dream of a somersaulting truck come true.

10.title: Good Bros and Goodbyes
10.plot: The Dieselsellerz SEMA build hits a snag, and the guys scramble to find a replacement. They decide to rebuild and give away their most iconic build: The Megaram.

101.title: Full of Bull
101.plot:

1.title: The Doubleheader: Game 1
1.plot: Heavy D, Diesel Dave and the Dieselsellerz crew work to reinvent the bullpen car for MLB Network, while working on their biggest commission ever- a Chevy Duramax for baseball legend Miguel Cabrera.

2.title: The Doubleheader: Game 2
2.plot: The pressure is on for the Dieselsellerz crew, when Detroit Tiger and baseball superstar Miguel Cabrera requests a tricked-out Chevy Duramax to be built for his charity. The guys aim to try and knock it out of the park with National League themed UTV bullpen car for MLB Network.

3.title: Dear Diary
3.plot: The Muscle and Diesel Dave rewrite Heavy D's autobiography, Heavy D takes the Megaram out on a rescue and ends up stuck in the mud, and Heavy D and Diesel Dave need Redbeard's help.

4.title: Race Against the Machine
4.plot: Heavy D, Diesel Dave and the Dieselsellerz crew scramble to finish an F100 race truck in time to race the legendary Mint 400, and Heavy D has the biggest giveaway yet- of the Mighty Megaram.

5.title: 3 Axels and a Baby
5.plot: The Dieselsellerz are pulling out all the stops to completely rebuild the Super Six for a client, and Diesel Dave leaves the nest- with a wife, a baby, and his very own client build- a 6.7 Powerstroke F450 Superduty built to tow anything.

6.title: Snow Job
6.plot: The Dieselsellerz are pulling out all the stops to completely rebuild the Super Six for a client, and Heavy D faces a challenge when his neighbor asks him to turn a 5-ton military truck into a snow-demolishing plow.

7.title: Clash of the Titan
7.plot: The Dieselsellerz are pulling out all the stops to build a new giveaway- a Nissan Titan w near-zero emission Cummins engine, and Heavy D fulfills his lifelong dream to drive a truck in Monster Jam.

8.title: Wham, Bam, C10 Slam
8.plot: A big new client asks Heavy D, Diesel Dave and the Dieselsellerz crew to turn a busted 1969 Chevy C10 into a diesel-drinking low-rider; the guys run into a perfect fix and flip Prolite race truck, which Heavy tests at a local dirt track.

9.title: Thunder or Lightning
9.plot: For the Dieselsellerz giveaway, Thunder vs. Lightning, two lifted F450s compete and the winner decides which one to take home; the guys continue turning a busted '69 Chevy C10 into a diesel low rider for a millionaire client.

10.title: Not So Easy Rider
10.plot: The guys face a huge challenge when a big dollar collector asks them to slam a 1969 Chevy C10; Heavy D and the guys are off to bike week at Sturgis to check out a one-of-a-kind hydro-static diesel motorcycle.

11.title: Bros to the Rescue!
11.plot: When the local Sheriff asks for a new Search and Rescue vehicle, the guys are excited to build an amphibious Sisu Nasu. And the diesel guys pull out all the stops for their next work truck giveaway- a Dodge 5500 with all the bells and whistles.

12.title: Hurricanes, Trucks and Snowmobiles
12.plot: When Heavy D adds a second truck to their latest giveaway, he comes up with an insane stunt to promote it- a race across a lake on snowmobiles. And the guys head to Houston with giant diesel trucks and supplies to help Hurricane Harvey victims.

imdb.plot outline: A group of friends in Utah own and operate a business that specializes in all things diesel. These guys don't just sell parts for diesel trucks and jeeps, they also design and build some of the biggest, baddest, and most amazing diesel powered vehicles you will ever see. Watch as they create these awesome masterpieces of American craftsmanship and enjoy all the antics they get into while doing it.
